description: This year we are seeing a lot of improvement from Fallon West. She has been doing tag matches and picking up moves from team mates and it shows in this match. Adley Rose is nothing to sneeze at. She comes in as an absolute rookie, never wrestling in her life and she gives a very impressive performance. With a little more coaching both these girls are going to be outstanding wrestlers and strap on fuckers!
title: Look out for this Rookie!!
